Task 1 – Digital Literacy Infographic Brief Description

This task involved creating an infographic to explain the concept of digital literacy and its importance in today’s digital world. The infographic highlights key aspects such as safe internet practices, maintaining a professional online presence, and following proper email etiquette. The goal of this task was to present important digital literacy concepts in a clear and visually engaging way so that they are easy to understand for a wider audience. The infographic was designed using Canva.
